<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَذِي أُذُنٍ بِلاَ سَمْعٍ * وَلاَ بَصَرٍ وَلاَ وَعْيِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَمَنْ يُبْصِرْهُ عَنْ ظَمَأٍ * يَنَلْ مَا شَاءَ مِنْ رِيِّ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَا هِيَ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَلْفَيْتُهَا عُرْيَانَةً * لَمْ تَسْتَتِرْ بِحُلَّةِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قَبَّلْتُهَا فَقَهْقَهَتْ * تَضْحَكُ لي مِنْ قُبْلَتي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَمْ أَزَلْ مُقَبِّلاً * حَتىَّ رَوَيْتُ غُلَّتي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حَبِيبَتي تِلْكَ وَمَا * قَصَدْتُ غَيرَ <span class="c3">{٠٠٠}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{محَمَّدٌ الأَسْمَر}</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
