<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَاتِنَةٌ مُهَذَّبَة * مِنْ نَشْوَةٍ مُرَكَّبَة<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>تَوَسَّدَتْ أَنَامِلِي * وَاسْتَسْلَمَتْ مُلْتَهِبَة<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَعَرْبَدَتْ عَلَى فَمِي * أَنْفَاسُهَا المُضْطَرِبَة<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَظَلُّ وَهْيَ في يَدِي * مُبْعَدَةً مُقَرَّبَة<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَكُلَّمَا أَدْنَيْتُهَا * لِلَّحْظَةِ المُسْتَعْذَبَة<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تحْمَرُّ مِن حَيَائِهَا * وَجْنَتُهَا المُخَضَّبَة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَهَبْتُهَا لِصَاحِبي * فَلَمْ يَرُدَّ لي الهِبَة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تجِيئُني فِضِّيَّةً * وَتَارَةً مُذَهَّبَة<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>